IGHT”</strong>演唱的动画《<a href="http://yorimoi.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">比宇宙更远的地方</a>》片尾曲<strong>《Kokokara，Kokokara</strong> 》的歌曲翻唱视频。此外，视频还真实描绘了三人前往南极洲的情景。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[从这里，从这里//Koko Kara，Koko Kara] LAZULIGHT IN ANTARCTICA ver. 封面：LazuLight" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H5kC-4MGEK4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>三人乘坐一架从日本出发的南极旅行航班出发。一路上，我们乘船游览，用相机捕捉到了冰原、企鹅群、鲸鱼等景观。他们还带来了一张剪有LAZULIGHT粉丝艺术的纸，在南极洲雄伟的大自然背景下，仿佛LAZULIGHT与粉丝一起旅行。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.bcpory8k8112-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.bcpory8k8112-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.bcpory8k8112-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.bcpory8k8112-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.bcpory8k8112-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.9mzkvd1obh0y-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.9mzkvd1obh0y-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.9mzkvd1obh0y-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.9mzkvd1obh0y-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/11fb99a923bf179cea0454c09792cc67-kix.9